  <li id="comment-21577" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://eveatetheapple.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Marisa</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/09/before-you-know-it/#comment-21577"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-09-12T01:02:11-04:00">Sunday, September 12, 2010 at 1:02 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Leeks never get enough credit. It&#39;s as though they are the slightly unfashionable relative in the onion family. I adore leeks with vinaigrette. It&#39;s lovely to see them gain the spotlight for once!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
