    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Holy Cow &#8211; Mustard loses its potency?  Who knew?</p>
<p>I, too, adore leeks.  One of my favorite leek recipes is to cook down equal amounts of chopped leeks and chopped fresh tomatoes with some fennel (I use dried but I am sure fresh would be wonderful as well) &#8211; when they have become appropriately saucy and lost some of their liquid, I add balsamic vinegar.  Lovely.</p>
    </div>

